    üõãÔ∏è Layout:
    
    Background image aligned left, featuring a lifestyle shot (sofa + interior setting).
    On the right half, include a text container with:
    A large heading (e.g., ‚ÄúWelcome to Honeypot‚Äù)
    A paragraph of descriptive brand story text (2‚Äì3 sentences)
    üñäÔ∏è Merchant Controls:
    
